<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Brass: Lancashire - Incompatible Game</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/lobby" class="nav-brand">Brass: Lancashire</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/lobby" class="nav-link">Lobby</a>
      <a href="/wiki" class="nav-link">Wiki</a>
      <a href="/profile" class="nav-link">Stats</a>
      <a href="/account" class="nav-user"><%= user.username %></a>
      <form method="POST" action="/logout" style="display:inline">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm">Logout</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <main class="container">
    <div class="incompatible-notice">
      <h2>Game No Longer Playable</h2>
      <p>This game (<strong><%= game.name %></strong>) was created with version <strong><%= gameVersion %></strong>, which is not compatible with the current version <strong><%= currentVersion %></strong>.</p>
      <p>The game rules or data structure changed in a way that makes it impossible to continue this game. Please start a new game.</p>
      <a href="/lobby" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Lobby</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
